    Abyssal Protocol stockpile category safety pass.
    Adds explicit ThingCategory membership to ABY item-like defs that relied on parent inheritance
    or had no explicit category in the source XML. This improves stockpile/filter compatibility
    in large modpacks and avoids resources/rewards becoming unstorable.
